        "title": "ui(i18n): localize chat page slash commands and composer for zh-CN",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Problem: Chat page slash command palette and composer had hardcoded English strings when using Simplified Chinese locale.\r\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see English labels, descriptions, and hints in the chat command menu, footer shortcuts, Talk status, and search box.\r\n- What changed: Extracted all hardcoded strings from `ui/src/ui/views/chat.ts` and `ui/src/ui/views/command-palette.ts` into i18n keys, added translations to both `en.ts` and `zh-CN.ts`. Added `getLocalizedCommandDescription()` and `getLocalizedArgChoice()` in `slash-commands.ts` to localize command descriptions and arg choices at render time without affecting tests.\r\n- What did NOT change (scope boundary): No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No new features added. No other locales touched. Backend command definitions remain in English.\r\n\r\n## Change Type (select all)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Bug fix\r\n- [ ] Feature\r\n- [ ] Refactor required for the fix\r\n- [ ] Docs\r\n- [ ] Security hardening\r\n- [x] Chore/infra\r\n\r\n## Scope (select all touched areas)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Gateway / orchestration\r\n- [ ] Skills / tool execution\r\n- [ ] Auth / tokens\r\n- [ ] Memory / storage\r\n- [ ] Integrations\r\n- [ ] API / contracts\r\n- [x] UI / DX\r\n- [ ] CI/CD / infra\r\n\r\n## Linked Issue/PR\r\n\r\n- Closes #\r\n- Related #\r\n- [ ] This PR fixes a bug or regression\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof (required for external PRs)\r\n\r\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Chat page command palette, slash menu footer, arg choices, Talk status, and search placeholder were not localized to Simplified Chinese.\r\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (`pnpm gateway:dev`).\r\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI assets with `pnpm ui:build`, started gateway, opened Control UI Chat tab, typed `/` to open slash command menu.\r\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot — command categories (会话 / 模型 / 代理 / 工具), command descriptions, footer shortcuts (导航 / 补全 / 运行 / 选择 / 关闭), arg choices, and Talk options all render in Chinese.\r\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows fully translated chat slash command UI.\r\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"2460\" height=\"1138\" alt=\"8\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/86e053e1-52f5-4914-80b6-4dc8053ee452\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n## Root Cause (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A — not a bug fix.\r\n\r\n## Regression Test Plan (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A — not a bug fix or regression.\r\n\r\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\r\n\r\n- Chat page slash command UI now fully localized to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\r\n- Command arg choices (e.g., `/tts` sub-options) now display in Chinese.\r\n- English locale unchanged (new keys added, existing behavior preserved).\r\n\r\n## Diagram (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n## Security Impact (required)\r\n\r\n- New permissions/capabilities? (`No`)\r\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (`No`)\r\n- New/changed network calls? (`No`)\r\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (`No`)\r\n- Data access scope changed? (`No`)\r\n- If any `Yes`, explain risk + mitigation:\r\n\r\n## Repro + Verification\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\n\r\n- OS: macOS\r\n- Runtime/container: Node 22 (local dev)\r\n- Model/provider: N/A\r\n- Integration/channel (if any): N/A\r\n- Relevant config (redacted): N/A\r\n\r\n### Steps\r\n\r\n1. `pnpm ui:build` to build Control UI assets\r\n2. `pnpm gateway:dev` to start local gateway\r\n3. Open Control UI in browser, navigate to Chat tab\r\n4. Switch locale to zh-CN (if not already)\r\n5. Type `/` in the composer to open slash command menu\r\n6. Select a command with arg choices (e.g., `/tts`) to verify sub-options\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\n\r\n- Command category labels display in Chinese: 会话, 模型, 代理, 工具\r\n- Command descriptions display in Chinese\r\n- Footer shortcuts display in Chinese: 导航, 补全, 运行, 选择, 关闭\r\n- Arg choices display in Chinese\r\n- Talk status and options display in Chinese\r\n- Search placeholder displays in Chinese: 搜索消息...\r\n\r\n### Actual\r\n\r\n- All above verified locally.\r\n\r\n## Evidence\r\n\r\n- [ ] Failing test/log before + passing after\r\n- [ ] Trace/log snippets\r\n- [x] Screenshot/recording\r\n- [ ] Perf numbers (if relevant)\r\n\r\n**Before**\r\n<img width=\"2886\" height=\"1442\" alt=\"5\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b90404e8-dc4f-428e-ac7a-099476d42eb9\" />\r\n<img width=\"2902\" height=\"1296\" alt=\"7\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ee78fa67-a75f-458d-9f43-499e4f207716\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n**After**\r\n<img width=\"2460\" height=\"1138\" alt=\"8\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/620118d4-9a8b-4ecb-b9e8-677b0b61e28d\" />\r\n<img width=\"2444\" height=\"998\" alt=\"9\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/87a05368-e38e-4bde-8ef7-ecf412fc7ce7\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n## Human Verification (required)\r\n\r\n- Verified scenarios: Chat tab slash command menu, arg picker, footer shortcuts, Talk status, search placeholder in zh-CN locale.\r\n- Edge cases checked: English locale still renders correctly (new keys added to en.ts).\r\n- What you did **not** verify: Other non-English locales.\r\n\r\n## Review Conversations\r\n\r\n- [x] I replied to or resolved every bot review conversation I addressed in this PR.\r\n- [x] I left unresolved only the conversations that still need reviewer or maintainer judgment.\r\n\r\n## Compatibility / Migration\r\n\r\n- Backward compatible? (`Yes`)\r\n- Config/env changes? (`No`)\r\n- Migration needed? (`No`)\r\n- If yes, exact upgrade steps:\r\n\r\n## Risks and Mitigations\r\n\r\nNone.\r\n",
